quran[75]{c,v,t}:
  87,1,"Tlotlisa lebitso la Mohlokomeli-Mong`a hau, Ea Okametseng Tsohle"
  87,2,"Ea hlotseng, Ea faneng ka taelo"
  87,3,"Ea hlomathitseng melao, Ea fanang ka tataiso"
  87,4,Ea hlahisang lekhulo
  87,5,Hamorao le fetohe lehlare
  87,6,"Ka mekhahlelo Re u ruta ho bala, hore u se ke oa lebala"
  87,7,"Kantle ho thato ea Allah, hoba U tseba tse pepeneneng le tse sephiring"
  87,8,Re tla nolofatsa tsela e u lebisang tseleng e otlolohileng
  87,9,"Ka hona fana ka keletso, ha keletso e le molemo"
  87,10,Keletso e tla amoheloa ke ba nang le ts’abo
  87,11,Empa e tla qobjoa ke ba malimabe
  87,12,Ba tlang ho kena Khanareng ea Mollo
  87,13,Oo kahara ona ba sa tlong ho shoa kapa ho phela
  87,14,Ba tla atleha ke ba itlhoekisang
  87,15,"Ba rorisa lebitso la Mohlokomeli-Mong`a bona, ka thapelo"
  87,16,"Che, le khetha bophelo ba lefats’e lena"
  87,17,"Empa bophelo Bo-tlang bo molemo, ha bo fele"
  87,18,"Ka sena se har’a mangolo a mathomo, –"
  87,19,Mangolo a Abrahama le Moshe
  88,1,Na nalane ea timelo e ile ea u fihlela
  88,2,Lifahleho tse ling li tla phoqeha mohla tsatsi leo
  88,3,"Li be mats’oenyehong, li tepelle, –"
  88,4,Li kene lelakabeng la Mollo
  88,5,"Khabareng ba fuoe metsi, a belang ho noa, ho tsoa Selibeng se belang"
  88,6,"Ha ba na ho fumana lijo, haese litholoana tse babang"
  88,7,"Tse sa tlong ho aha ‘mele, kapa ho khorisa"
  88,8,Lifahleho tse ling li tla nyakalla mohla oo
  88,9,Ke thabo ho latela ts’ebetso ea bona
  88,10,Serapeng se phahameng
  88,11,Moo ba ke keng ba utloa lipuo tse hlohlonts’ang litsebe
  88,12,Moo Seliba se kopotsang
  88,13,Moo Li-Terone tse phahameng li leng teng
  88,14,Mepotjoana e behiloeng
  88,15,Mesangoana e behiloeng ka mekhahlelo
  88,16,Le meseme e nonofetseng
  88,17,Ha ba bone kamoo likamele li hlotsoeng
  88,18,Kamoo leholimo le phahamisitsoeng
  88,19,Le kamoo lithaba li tsepamisitsoeng
  88,20,Le kamoo lefats’e le aliloeng
  88,21,"Kahoo ba hlomekomelise, hobane u mohlokomelisi"
  88,22,Ha u molebeli oa litaba tsa bona
  88,23,"Empa ha mong a furalla, a latola Allah"
  88,24,Allah u tla mo ahlola ka kotlo e boima
  88,25,Poelo ea bona e ho Rona
  88,26,"Ho ho Rona, ho ba biletsa maikarabellong"
  89,1,Ka meso
  89,2,Le ka masiu a leshome
  89,3,Le ka libopuoa tsohle tsa Allah
  89,4,Le ka bosiu ha bo esa
  89,5,Holim’a lits’upiso tsena ho teng bopaki ho ba utloisisang
  89,6,Na ha u elelloe kamoo Mong`a hau A ileng A sebetsa kateng ka morabe oa Ba-Ad
  89,7,"Ba motse oa Iram, ka lits’ia tse phahameng"
  89,8,Bao ho es’ong ho be le tlholeho e ts’oanang le’a bona lefats’eng
  89,9,Joaloka morabe oa Ba – Thamude o ileng oa betla majoe kahar’a phula
  89,10,"Le Faro, Morena oa Lipalo"
  89,11,Bao kaofela ha bona ebileng batloli ba meeli eohle holim’a lefats’e
  89,12,Le hona ho fehla lehloeo kahar’a tsona
  89,13,Mong`a hau U ile A ts’ollela sekhobo sa kahlolo ea Hae holim’a bona
  89,14,Ruri! Ha ho se patehileng ho Mong`a hau
  89,15,"Joaloka motho eo ereng ha Mong`a hae A mo leka ka ho mo neha hlompho, A bile A ba lereko malebana le eena, e be o re: “Mong`a ka U mphile hlompho.”"
  89,16,"Empa hang ha A mo neha teko ka ho khutsufatsa mekhoa ea bophelo ba hae, o re: “Mong`a ka U ntlontlolotse.”"
  89,17,Che! Empa lona le hloloa ho hauhela khutsana
  89,18,Ha le khothaletsane phepo ea mafutsana
  89,19,Le ja mafa lekemekeme ka bonyollo bohle
  89,20,Le bile le rata leruo ka lerato le hlollang
  89,21,Che! mohla lefats’e le fetohang lehlohlojane le thumisehileng
  89,22,Mong`a hau A theoha le manyeloi a entse mekhahlelo ka mekhahlelo
  89,23,"Le lihele li atametsoa haufinyane; Ruri! Ke mohla motho a tlang ho hopola, empa mohopolo oo o tla mo thusa kang"
  89,24,"Motho o tla re: “Ao! Hoja ke mpile ka etsa letsete molemong oa bophelo ba ka!”"
  89,25,Ruri! O tla ahloloa ka kahlolo es’o kang e bonoa mohla letsatsi leo
  89,26,Ebile ha ho ea tlamang kamoo A tlamang kateng
  89,27,"Ho tla thoe hoba lokileng: “Oho lona! Meea ea lona ha e ke e phomole ka khotso"
  89,28,Khutlelang ho Mong`a lona le khotsofetse monyakeng o molemo oa Hae
  89,29,Kenang kahar’a makhabunyane a Ka
  89,30,Kahar’a serapa sa Ka!”